description:
Matt Catingub Big Band feat Mavis Rivers - 1991 - I'm Getting Cement All Over Ewe

'90 big band date spotlighting Catingub's current orchestra. The ensemble sections are polished, and the CD sound is wonderful. But the Catingub originals are very derivative, and the band lacks the great soloist that can rise above the fray and elevate the orchestra in the process. Mavis Rivers contributes some enthusiastic vocals. (AllMusic)
